column1:
How you can eat five bowls of rice is beyond
me... Is your stomach a black hole or
something?

Look, if they're offering free refills, then you
can bet I'm orderin' 'em.

Indeed. You can eat the first bowl and focus
exclusively on the glistening of the meat, then
the aroma on the next, and so on.
Pretty sure that's just you, dude.

Well, I will say the food here certainly
is delicious!
It was, as they say, "a piece of cake."

Guess we should leave where we eat up to
Sophia now, huh?
Hm? What's goin' on over there?

Natsume-san, your latest issue was just
amazing, as always!

Natsume-san, over here! Can you please sign
my copy!?

Heheh. Thank you for all your support. Whoa,
hold on now, only one autograph per person,
please.

Oh, my apologies, but could the men please
go to the back of the line? Ladies first, you see.

He looks pretty popular. I heard that woman
say "latest book." Does that mean he's a writer?

Hello there. Are you looking for an autograph
as well? Or perhaps a handshake?

Oh, how terribly rude of me to keep such
lovely fans waiting...

Please, accept this as a token of my apology,
yes? Don't worry, I've already signed it.
Listen, uh... We were just passing by...

Ah, is that so? It seems I got a little ahead of
myself.
Yours truly. Ango Natsume. It's a pleasure.

"Prince of Nightmares." That's the name from
those flyers on the Masamune statue.

My flyers on Masamune's statue? Ah, I think I
know what happened...

That's most likely the work of some of my
more zealous fans. I appreciate them 
promoting my work, but...

It appears they went overboard somewhat.
Honestly, they can be a real handful 
sometimes.

Allow me to apologize on their behalf.
In exchange, allow me to offer you a kiss...

Yo, back off, dude. Can't you see you're
makin' her uncomfortable?
And who are you supposed to be?

I believe I was addressing these lovely young
ladies here. I'd thank you not to interrupt.

Sorry, but they're with us. You got a problem,
you can always talk to me.

Do you seriously think you can get away with
speaking to me like that?

Hah. My, this one's got some backbone,
doesn't he!?
Mr. Natsume, we need to get moving soon.

Well, then. It seems I must be going. I've a
magazine interview to get to.

To all those who have read my book, I thank
you from the bottom of my heart.

Oh, he's just so dreamy... I'll have to buy ten
more copies tomorrow to show him just how
much I care.

I dunno if he's some local bigshot or whatever,
but he sure was pissin' me off.

He was a strange one, for sure. But the people
around him seemed really happy. Why was
that?

I must agree. He wasn't at all deserving of such
praise, even in the form of flattery.
Mhm... I was just a little surprised, is all.

How'd a jerk like him get so popular? It doesn't
make any sense!
There might be something else going on here.
He could even be changing people's hearts...

You mean... He's the Monarch of the Sendai
Jail?

No, I think you might be on to something.
If he's the Monarch, then everything else
totally makes sense!
We'll need to look into this.

Perf, I got my laptop back at the RV. Should be
able to dig something up from there.
